<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>EmailCodeTemplate</title>
</head>
<body style="width: 700px; height: 700px; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; color: black">
<div style="padding: 12px; border-radius: 12px; background-color: #eef6f6;">
    <p style="text-align: center">勉強！</p>
</div>
<div style="padding: 12px; border-radius: 12px; background-color: rgb(245,245,245); margin-top: 12px;">
    <h3>Hello, {{name}}!</h3>
    <br/>
    <p>We sent you this email because you've requested to reset your password</p>
    <p>To continue and reset your password click on the link below:</p>
    <br/>
    <a style="padding: 12px; background-color: lightgray; display: inline-block; border-radius: 12px;"
       href="{{resetLink}}">Click</a>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <p>If you don't know, where this email came from, please, delete it.</p>
    <p>This is an autogenerated email, please, do not reply.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>